title: 3drcracing 1.0
description: 3D RC RACING: Is a Radio Controlled Racing game. Race with friends on tracks you made using our easy track builder. Use your own Hobby level radio and receiver for ultimate control. Smash and bash in Multiplayer game play up to 10 people and AI. Set up your car with simple features that can make a difference in how your car hooks to the track. Community designed for online racing that you can control. In game Lobby so you can find and race anyone. Advanced Mod Tool Kit to build tracks and design your own cars. Developed by Red Hill Games USA.
